headline: Why Dollar Tree (DLTR) Stock Is Trading Up Today
summary: Shares of discount treasure-hunt retailer Dollar Tree (NASDAQ:DLTR) jumped 3.5% in the afternoon session after JPMorgan raised its price target on the company's shares to $113 from $100.
